{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "雪夜獨行", "storyInfo": "埃琳娜想方設法還原了天災前夜觀測到的異樣資訊，發現有“天外來物”墜落在了謝拉格。為尋找真相，也為尋找失蹤的卡羅琳，埃琳娜獨自離開了觀測站。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>謝拉格-萊茵生命觀測站 </><p=2>1101年12月7日</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格天災發生前三十三小時"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儀器正常，終端電量充足，筆芯和稿紙充足……還有足夠的咖啡，好！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "熟悉的通宵之夜就要開始囉——"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "哇啊啊！"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜被房間角落裡傳來的窸窸窣窣的聲音嚇了一跳，她這才發現即使在這個時間自己也不是觀測間唯一的使用者。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rollpaper", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接著，儀器旁邊成堆的廢稿紙裡爬出了一個人。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……埃琳娜，是你啊。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哈欠）……我就想說這個時間點還有哪個想追求麥克斯獎的大科學家在工作呢……", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你是卡羅琳前輩？！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您竟然，還記得我？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能量科最年輕的明星研究員，不要太小看自己的名氣了。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您過獎了……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為您已經回去了，我看排班表上今天應該是我來記錄觀測才對——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧，計劃進度什麼時候跟著排班表走過——不然我也不會在這裡住了半個月了。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "怪不得來觀測站以後，都沒見過您幾次……"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "埃琳娜", "content": "辛苦了。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回來的感覺怎麼樣？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說……？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再次回到萊茵生命。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這次觀測站計劃開始組織人手的時候，我第一個就想到了你，但我本來以為，你會拒絕的。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……說實話，我也猶豫過。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，萊茵生命曾經給了我很珍貴的機會，而且，我從來都沒有懷疑過，萊茵生命本身是個很偉大的科技公司。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我至今還是覺得，在萊茵學習的那段時間，是我離自己的夢想最近的時候。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我也得承認……哪怕是斐爾迪南，在科學研究領域，他的才華確實讓人羨慕。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，他確實有一個好用的物理腦子，那就讓他去做適合他做的事吧。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正從特區監獄裡出來以後，他就全心投入了他的研究，也沒空去欺負別的研究員了。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看能量科主任這個位置用不了多久就該變動一下了……小埃琳娜，加油哦。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不！那太誇張了——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想，來仔細看看……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "cg_moonmasked", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜下意識地仰起頭，透過觀測站透明的穹頂，她看到了被風雪遮蔽的天空。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她討厭這樣的感覺。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像她討厭家族裡那些古舊的傳統與認知，那些曾經阻擋在她面前的、所有與科學本身無關的阻礙。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她相信科學理應在純粹的環境裡不斷突破，解開人們對於這片大地的每一個疑問……"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次觀測站的計劃，是非常非常難得的機會。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想專心地做我的研究，如果有可能的話，可以在已有知識的邊界上，走得再遠一點……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邊界啊……這裡還真是離“邊界”最近的地方。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你聽說過謝拉格的傳說嗎？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說？什麼傳說？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片土地一千年來從來沒有遭受過天災，是因為有神明保護這裡。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……每個國家早期都有過將特殊的現象歸因於“神明”的傳統啦。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是謝拉格相對隔絕的環境讓這樣的傳說保留的時間長了一點……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是從考察結果來看，謝拉格確實至少一千年沒有遭遇過天災呢。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#4$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確是很少見的情況……但也一定是有可以解釋的理由的。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想最大的可能應該是謝拉格的高海拔環境導致源石粉塵沉降無法集中，或者是——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻巨獸？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩就不要用這種神秘學笑話來調侃我啦，我很認真在做假設的！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道這片大地上還有許多地方保留著關於巨獸的傳說和想像——一種體型等同於山脈的古老巨物，在死後身軀也會化為山川湖泊。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不說根本沒有可信的、能證實巨獸存在的記錄，而且，如果真的有這樣的生物存在，那維持牠們生命活動的能量從何而來呢？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩怎麼突然提起這個……？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼，閒聊時突然想到罷了。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，就先聊到這裡吧。去休息吧，晚上的觀測交給我來就好。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的可以嗎？可是前輩已經連續好幾晚值夜班了——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正作息已經顛倒過來了，和你聊了一下天，正好清醒了一點。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒記錯的話，高能粒子束轟擊裝置的供能結構應該還有問題沒解決吧？", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？前輩這麼瞭解……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "養足精神，把你聰明的大腦用在更有價值的地方。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就，多謝前輩啦！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等您有空的時候，我請您吃山下新開的維多利亞餐廳的炸鱗薯條！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧，沒有一個維多利亞人會想在異國他鄉吃到正宗的維多利亞食物的。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……那還是請您去吃謝拉格特色的起司鍋吧。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一言為定。", "name": "卡羅琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1999_1#3$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_r1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_labamb", "loop": "false", "channel": "aa", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "aa", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "卡羅琳"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夜深人靜，謝拉格又一個平常的夜晚。這片古老的土地早已入睡，燈火為星光讓位。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夜幕中沉眠的雪山或許偶爾引人遐想，但更多的人早已習慣了她的懷抱。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的夜晚，還會觀望夜空的人並不多。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_l", "rox": 55.0, "roy": 89.0, "roz": 75.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "卡羅琳"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是……！", "name": "卡羅琳"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是各種儀器還是她的肉眼，都清楚地觀測到了那道劃過天際的異樣光芒。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宛若天啟。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從資料來看，卡羅琳女士確實是一位優秀聰明、前途無量的年輕研究員。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命和哥倫比亞都很重視這個計劃，不是什麼人都能加入的。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前來說，她的記錄和通訊內容並沒有查到問題。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是維多利亞出身？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能為你提供更多她的私人資訊了，這違反了萊茵生命的基礎人權隱私規定。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在謝拉格方面正式提起間諜訴訟之前，我們只能提供她在萊茵生命的資訊給你。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我只是確認一下。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她提交的申請很齊全，每次值班和外勤的資訊收集這些事都做得很好……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據記錄來看，她甚至主動為自己申請了一份外勤探索工作。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在完成基礎科學研究任務的同時，還能順便收集一些謝拉格的地理資訊？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是一個盡職的研究員，在萊茵生命的工作評價一直很好，在學校時的學業成績也很好。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按理來說，這樣的研究員並不會捲入目前的麻煩中。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但事實就是，到目前為止，我們依然找不到任何關於卡羅琳去向的線索與資訊。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……無論你是否相信，萊茵生命方面都比你更想找到卡羅琳的下落。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這關乎著許多事，例如萊茵生命的聲譽、研究數據的資訊安全、管理系統的漏洞與滲透，我們雙方的商業合作與後續的信任關係，以及……", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及……謝拉格本身的發展。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是您從科學倫理道德共識委員會的立場提出的考量？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望這樣說不會引起您的誤會，這並不是出於居高臨下的關懷，我十分尊重喀蘭貿易的事業。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，從故步自封中走出的勇氣是科學家最應該讚賞的特質。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該不只有科學家是這樣吧。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在謝拉格，人們常說黑色的馱獸是不溫馴的。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠們會一次又一次跳出圍欄，奔向雪原之中。當牧人循著牠們的足跡走入雪原，便再也不會回來。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們死了嗎？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“走入雪原再也沒回來”在謝拉格差不多就是那個意思。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一頁又一頁紙放在桌面上，卡羅琳的筆記和行動最終只匯聚成了這樣小小的一疊。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但出走的黑馱獸去了哪裡呢？這實際上是同一個問題。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許，牠帶著牧人走向雪山，迷失在森林，凍死在了一個夜裡。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的紙頁被閱讀完畢，也落下來。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或許……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯放下最後一張提交記錄。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白覆蓋白，像是新雪覆蓋在凍結的山壁上。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們只是找到了一處新的水源，看見了新的天地。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，能告訴我那些外勤探索任務的詳細位置嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_keyboard_console", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "key"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "key", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electronicbuzz"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，觀測數據毀損得太徹底了，無法從記錄終端還原儲存的內容……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桌面上各種文件堆疊，馬克杯裡還殘留著乾涸的咖啡漬。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修復失敗的電子提示音讓心臟再一次下沉。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出入記錄都有ID卡證明，宿舍和實驗室也沒有找到任何留言……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主要的監視攝影機壞了，實驗室側邊的兩個監視器都沒有拍攝到任何內容……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，一切都太過巧合，難道真的是卡羅琳前輩她……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不能這麼想，現在人人都覺得她就是間諜，我向繆爾賽思主任申請查閱權限為的就是調查清楚，如果連我也這樣先入為主……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咚咚，有一直熬夜的人在嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆……繆爾賽思主任？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到我來，你很意外嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽大家說你已經兩個晚上沒回宿舍了……還在研究丟失的資料嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在基本能夠確認，我們看到的觀測記錄的確是被修改過的。雖然我還不能確定，到底是誰，出於什麼目的修改了數據。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是我有理由相信，那段被掩蓋的數據，一定藏著非常關鍵的線索……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "繆爾賽思", "content": "唔……不過……"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "繆爾賽思", "content": "算了，不提這個，我帶了點心。先吃點東西吧，肚子餓的時候腦子是轉不動的。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您，這是……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格乳酪餅，加了糖霜和山莓子果醬，之前一段時間觀測站裡還蠻流行的，你沒吃過嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小組裡的人有提到過，但前一陣子忙著調查謝拉格特殊能源的課題沒能下山，本來是想下山去吃起司鍋時，順路買一點吃吃看的。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜拿起一塊橢圓形的小餅，放了一段時間的麵餅有些乾燥，因為加熱過，裡面的起司和果醬依然保有流動性。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處水流沖洗的聲音停下，繆爾賽思拿著兩個乾淨的馬克杯在她的身邊坐了下來。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能一起喝點咖啡嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洗乾淨的杯子裡重新倒入咖啡，香氣瀰漫在空氣中。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實驗室中機器運作的聲音在深夜十分清晰，牆壁上巨大的窗口清澈透明，謝拉格的星空一如既往無垠而深遠。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊繃的氣氛漸漸放鬆下來，埃琳娜猶豫片刻，端起杯子。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀……在深夜的實驗室裡和後輩一起喝咖啡，這種日子真是讓人懷念呢。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#10$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您以前也經常熬夜嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做我們這行的，真的有人不熬夜嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說正式工作之後啦，還在讀書的時候，每次期末考我都覺得自己身體裡流淌的不是水，而是咖啡呢——", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……果然大家都是這樣想的嗎？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟晚上的工作效率比較高嘛。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，夜晚更安靜，某種情況下會讓人的注意力變得更好。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前太忙的時候，會一邊寫一份論文，一邊用錄音筆口述另一份論文的大綱。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣就可以同時處理兩份作業了，現在想想，還真是……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊，對了，錄音！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？什麼，什麼錄音？你要去哪裡？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監視器的錄音！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監視器畫面，查看權限，通過……時間是……凌晨的三點十九分……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到了，就是這裡。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你不是說，監視器沒有拍到實驗台的畫面嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對……但是監視器很有可能錄到了觀測儀器的聲音。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽……這裡有很多儀器工作的聲音，這個比較明顯的滴滴聲應該是聲波感測器，我聽得出來。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的播報頻率和繪圖直接相關，我們可以按照這個頻率來還原——抱歉，借過一下。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你要紙和筆嗎？在這裡。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊、謝謝。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sketchdraw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "筆尖摩擦紙面，整日與儀器相伴的研究員對數據無比熟悉。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她將用筆記錄下來的數字輸入了電腦，接著……"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_keyboard_console", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "key"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "key", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_medicalbeep", "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_line_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 6.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有了……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是被隱藏起來的那段數據。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……從這個圖像來看……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在天災發生的前一天凌晨，謝拉格的喀蘭聖山發生了一次微弱的地震。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對……不是地震，更像是遭受了一次巨大的撞擊。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像是，有某樣東西從天上……掉下來，掉落在謝拉格的山上……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後謝拉格就迎來了……第一場天災。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀測站中巨大而開闊的窗外，月色之下的雪山散發著一種幾近於透明的藍色，仍是謝拉格的夜。"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡羅琳行蹤不明，是去尋找這個“天外來物”了？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是她為什麼會選擇獨自行動？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡羅琳前輩從沒有這樣擅離職守過，她一定是發現了什麼……！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要找到那個東西的墜落點，我們也許就能找到她！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於那個“天外來物”的墜落點，按照撞擊聲的頻率，我們可以計算出詳細的位置！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……繆爾賽思主任，我們……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，現在的蔓珠院是不會為萊茵生命代理調查的。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理論上來說我們不應該再多插手這件事了。我們能做的最多就是把這件事上報給總轄構件科。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，卡羅琳前輩也許正在遭遇什麼危險……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該知道，這不是你的義務。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不算是卡羅琳的熟識。她的境遇本質上來說和你並無關係。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "片刻沉默之中，繆爾賽思把杯中殘留的冷咖啡一飲而盡。"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "苦澀的味道讓她輕輕吐了吐舌頭，隨手又拿起一塊小餅塞進嘴裡，一邊咀嚼一邊繼續開口。"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但是呢。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科學家最重要的才能，有時候正是那一點點的勇敢和……莽撞。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是一個敏銳的孩子，善於尋找音樂中的節拍。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是舞者的必需素養，如果綁著你，不讓你自由自在地行動，那也太殘忍了。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆爾賽思主任，您的意思是……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚沒有人知道我來找你，所以自然也沒有人會勸阻你，告訴你能怎麼做、不能怎麼做……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這份宵夜嘛……就當作是你自己從公用冰箱拿的，怎麼樣？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}